            <h2>Adapting to the New Systems</h2>
            <p>Tekken 6 introduced the Rage mechanic and Bound combo extensions, which completely transformed competitive play. I spent hundreds of hours mastering stage positioning and wall carry distances to maximize damage during critical tournament rounds.</p>
            
            <h3>Core Practice Routines</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Optimizing Bound conversions from standard launchers</li>
